---
title: Coconut Prawn Korma with Green Beans, Chickpeas and Rice
description: Easy-to-make, mild and healthy, this prawn curry recipe is a HelloFresh customer favourite. Chef Gaby has perfected the creamy curry sauce, gently combining coconut milk with our special korma spice blend and packing in lots of crunchy green beans to boost your five a day intake.
